      "text": "Want to read the guideline in your own time? Download the PDF Download full guideline Looking for a quick overview? Check the pocket guidelines. Download pocket guidelines Searching... 1. Introduction Introduction Methods Epidemiology Classification General Management Principals Urogenital Trauma Guidelines References Conflict Of Interest Citation Information Copyright And Terms Of Use",
